high_descs: Turn around to face the fridge and then turn left to move to stand at the end of the counter, facing the stove.
Pick up the butter knife closest to you from the counter.
Move around the counter to stand facing the loaf of bread left of the stove.
Use the knife to slice the apple by the loaf of bread.
Turn around, go straight a few steps, and then turn left to move to the counter space above the dishwasher.
Place the knife on the counter above the dishwasher.
Turn back around and head to the apple you just sliced left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter.
Carry the apple slice to stand in front of the fridge.
Place the apple slice in the fridge, close the door, and then remove after a couple seconds.
Turn back around and carry the apple slice to where you left the knife on the counter above the dishwasher.
Place the apple slice on the counter next to the egg.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of apple by the egg on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the countertop holding the loaf of bread
Take the knife under the bread
Go to the left of the stove
Cut the pepper
Go to the dishwasher
Place the knife down on the countertop
Go to the cut pepper
Take a slice of pepper
Go to the fridge
Chill the pepper
Go to the dishwasher
Place the pepper down on the countertop right of the knife
anns.task_desc: Move a knife and chilled pepper slice to a countertop

high_descs: Turn to the right, go forward, hang a left, go to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the left, go to the counter left of the stove.
Cut the apple that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left, go to the counter where the egg is.
Put the knife down on the counter by the egg.
Turn around, go forward, hang a right, go to the counter where the apple is.
Pick up a piece of the apple from the counter.
Turn around, go forward, hang a right, go to the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge and close the door, remove apple from the fridge once it is cold.
Turn to the left, go forward, hang a left, go to the counter where the egg is.
Put the apple on the counter in front of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put cold slice of apple on the counter.
